"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.4</span> 標題：籠頭（muzzle）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חסם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chasam（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:4\">DEU 25:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַחְסוֹם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： machsom)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:2\">PSA 39:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φιμός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： fimos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir20:29\">SIR 20:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sus1:60\">SUS 1:60</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φιμόω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： fimoō（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc1:35\">4MA 1:35</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κημόω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kēmoō（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:9\">1CO 9:9</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0318_muzzle.jpg\" alt=\"戴嘴套的牛進行穀物脫粒\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">戴嘴套的牛進行穀物脫粒 (Matson Collection, Library of Congress, Public domain)</figcaption></figure>籠頭是放在牲畜嘴上面或周圈的防護裝置，以防止牲畜撕咬或吃東西。籠頭是用繩子或皮條做成的網狀物件，這樣既不妨礙牲畜呼吸，又能阻止牠們吃東西。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>新約兩次提及這個詞都是在引用<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:4\">DEU 25:4</a> （其中<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:18</a> 依循《七十士譯本》，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:9\">1CO 9:9</a> 用的是對應的動詞）。有些語言可能需要使用描述性的語句來表達「籠住牛的嘴」，例如，「綁住牛的嘴，不讓牠吃東西」，或「蓋住牛的嘴，使牠不能吃東西」。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:2\">PSA 39:2</a> （《和》39:1），原文字面意為「我要用嚼環護住我的口」一句，可以譯成「我會保持沉默」，或「我一句話也不說」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文直譯）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
